        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 9. Dicerapanorpa triclada, genitalia, from Wolong, Sichuan. (A, B) Genital bulb of male, dorsal and ventral views; (C) same, ventral view with hypovalves removed; (D) aedeagus complex, ventral view; (E) subgenital plate of female, ventral view; (F–H) genital plate, dorsal, lateral and ventral views. Scale bars: A–C = 0.5 mm; D–H = 0.2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4608133/files/figure.png" .

